ITT sees tender , unit split done in Sept . ITT Corp on Wednesday said it expected to complete its proposed stock buyback and split of the company into three units by mid - to late September . Chairman Rand Araskog said the company had intensified its cost - cutting program and expected as much as $ 15 million more in savings on top of the $ 20 million in cuts already announced . " We ' re not done with the cost - reduction program yet , " he told analysts in a telephone conference call . 
